fields.About: MyMarket.com.bd is a new online marketplace in Bangladesh; this B2C marketplace has been launched in September, 2020. Throughout the last two years, MyMarket has been observing the Bangladeshi online shoppers & now it has started the online business and becoming popular online marketplace in Bangladesh-both for the buyers & the sellers. We have accommodated more than 150000 products from around 500 different categories on our Site already. Just visit our Site & find all your needs & wants under a single platform. Every day we are adding around 1000 products to our categories. More than 2000 top rated sellers are working with us; all these merchants are trusted names in the online market in Bangladesh. They provide high quality products at a reasonable price to the customers of MyMarket.com. Simultaneously we always check product quality & verify product price in the market before displaying them in front of our customers. The vast range of our products includes automobile accessories, motorcycle, bi-cycle & accessories, apparels, ornaments, watches, cosmetics, perfumes, shoes & sandals, mobile phones, electronics, household appliances, kitchen appliances, gadgets, computer & computer accessories, laptops, foods & beverages, sports items, books & CD, musical instruments, home decoration products & what not!
fields.policy: ["Data that we collect:  We may collect various pieces of information if you seek to place an order for a product with us on the Site.", "We collect- store- and process your data for processing your purchase on the Site and any possible later claims- and to provide you with our services. You undertake to treat the personal access data confidentially and not make it available to unauthorized third parties. We cannot assume any liability for the misuse of passwords unless this misuse is our fault.", "Other uses of your Personal Information: We may use your personal information for opinion and market research. Any answers to surveys or opinion polls we may ask you to complete will not be forwarded on to third parties. Disclosing your email address is only necessary if you would like to take part in competitions. However- anonymized data will not be capable of identifying you personally.", "Competitions: For any competition- we use the data to notify the winners and advertise our offers. Other than as set out in this Privacy Policy- we shall NOT sell or disclose your personal data to third parties without obtaining your prior consent unless this is necessary for the purposes set out in this Privacy Policy or unless we are required to do so by law. The Site may contain advertising of third parties and links to other sites or frames of other sites. Please be aware that we are not responsible for the privacy practices or content of those third parties or other sites- nor for any third party to whom we transfer your data in accordance with our Privacy Policy.", "Cookies: The acceptance of cookies is not a requirement for visiting the Site. However- we would like to point out that the use of the 'basket' functionality on the Site and ordering is only possible with the activation of cookies. Cookies are tiny text files that identify your computer to our server as a unique user when you visit certain pages on the Site and they are stored by your Internet browser on your computer's hard drive. Cookies can be used to recognize your Internet Protocol address- saving you time while you are on- or want to enter- the Site. We only use cookies for your convenience in using the Site (for example to remember who you are when you want to amend your shopping cart without having to re-enter your email address) and not for obtaining or using any other information about you (for example targeted advertising). Your browser can be set to not accept cookies- but this would restrict your use of the Site. Please accept our assurance that our use of cookies does not contain any personal or private details and are free from viruses. If you want to find out more information about cookies- go to http://www.allaboutcookies.org or to find out about removing them from your browser- go to http://www.allaboutcookies.org/manage-cookies/index.html.  This website uses Google Analytics- a web analytics service provided by Google- Inc. (\"Google\"). Google Analytics uses cookies- which are text files placed on your computer- to help the website analyze how users use the site. The information generated by the cookie about your use of the website (including your IP address) will be transmitted to and stored by Google on servers in the United States. Google will use this information for the purpose of evaluating your use of the website- compiling reports on website activity for website operators- and providing other services relating to website activity and internet usage. Google may also transfer this information to third parties where required to do so by law- or where such third parties process the information on Google's behalf. Google will not associate your IP address with any other data held by Google. You may refuse the use of cookies by selecting the appropriate settings on your browser- however- please note that if you do this you may not be able to use the full functionality of this website. By using this website- you consent to the processing of data about you by Google in the manner and for the purposes set out above.", "Security: We have in place appropriate technical and security measures to prevent unauthorized or unlawful access to or accidental loss of or destruction or damage to your information. When we collect data through the Site- we collect your personal details on a secure server. We use firewalls on our servers. Our security procedures mean that we may occasionally request proof of identity before we disclose personal information to you. You are responsible for protecting against unauthorized access to your password and to your computer.", "Your rights: If you are concerned about your data you have the right to request access to the personal data which we may hold or process about you. You have the right to require us to correct any inaccuracies in your data free of charge. At any stage- you also have the right to ask us to stop using your personal data for direct marketing purposes."]

fields.title: Cosmics Leather & tire Wax
fields.description:
Keep your interior & tire looking new with Kangaroo’s
leather care products. Kangaroo’s Cosmic Leather & Tire
Wax is all purpose wax for interiors, bumpers, various
types of leather and rubbers. It also brings back original
luster of tires and prevents tires from discoloration.
fields.key_features: ["Brings back original luster of interiors", "Easily applied", "leather and rubbers", "Prevention of discoloration", "Long lasting gloss effect"]

fields.title: Kangaroo Hard Excellent
fields.description:
Keep your car looking new with Kangaroo’s car wax.
Kangaroo’s Hard Excellent is suitable for easy and quick
wipe-down work for expensive metallic paints or dark
colors. It is formulated with 80% of carnauba wax on wax
composition to clean and protect in just one application.
It gives wet-look shine and long lasting effect.
 Carnauba wax creates a rich, warm glow. It does not
appear to sit on the paint. It transforms the paint into a
deep, liquid pool that shimmers under changing light
conditions. The more carnauba wax, the more shine.
fields.key_features: ["Easily applied", "No abrasives", "80% Carnauba wax on wax composition", "Lastingly protects against weathering effects"]

fields.title: Cosmic Easy car wax
fields.description:
Keep your car looking New with Kangaroo’s car was.
Kangaroo’s cosmic easy is suitable for easy  and Quick wipe down work for all colored cars. It is formulated with carnauba wax to prevent discolorations. Its gives wet-looks shine and long  Lasting effect.
fields.key_features: ["Easily applied", "Carnauba wax formula", "Lastingly  protect against weathering  Effect", "Prevention of Discoloration"]

fields.title: Kangaroo Profoam 2000
fields.description:
kangaroo’s profoam 2000 is a high Power Cleaner Which Cleans oil stains and grease on engine, various machinery parts, tools , greasy  trucks and big vehicles. It is also great  for hard , nonporous surfaces, including industrials floors.
Is a water soluble type which can be used  for coated Surfaces as well as bumpers and plastics.
fields.key_features: ["Multi use", "water based cleaner", "Wipes easily Stubborn grease and grime", "Non- flammable", "Non- Residue"]

fields.title: Engine cleaner
fields.description: Engine Cleaner, Aerosol Engine Cleaner - An effective tool for quickly and efficiently removing oil and grease from the engine surface. Before use, the container with the composition must be shaken thoroughly. Do not spray on a hot and wound engine. Avoid contact with electronic components, electrical connectors, sensors, etc. If it comes into contact with plastic, rinse or wipe it off quickly with a damp cloth. Mode of application: - Stop the engine and allow it to cool. - Shake the cleaner bottle thoroughly. - spray the product on the surface to be cleaned from a distance of 20-30 cm. - Wait 5-10 minutes and rinse with water or wipe with a damp cloth. - start the engine and let it dry.
fields.key_features: ["Remove  though grease and oil build up on Engine Surfaces", "Deep penetrating", "Improved performance and Fuel Efficient"]

fields.description: Product Description Kangaroo Car Shampoo: KANGARO CAR SHAMPOO safely lifts dirt, bugs and grime from car’s surfaces without stripping protective waxes with it’s pH balanced formula and unique foaming quality. Safe for all finishes. Rich foaming shampoo.

fields.title: Shoe polish NE(40g)
fields.description: Keep your shoes looking new with Kangaroo's shoe care product. Kangaroo's Shoe Polish is a all-season shoe polish for the care of your most valuable shoes. It is specially formulated to achieve glazing and a high gloss finish.  The quality and concentration of hard waxes used in the polish persist much longer than liquid polishes, allowing the shine of one's shoes to be easily renewed long after application by simply rebuffing.
